{"type": "article", "id": 49454, "title": "一款简洁的短途旅行包，几组有性格的桌椅｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-01-24T23:32:28Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 47228, "name": "SKAGEN"}, {"id": 47229, "name": "Adrenalina"}, {"id": 47230, "name": "Oliver Cabell"}, {"id": 331, "name": "John Lewis"}, {"id": 21508, "name": "Patternity"}, {"id": 47231, "name": "CARMENES"}, {"id": 47232, "name": "Italo Pertichini"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 107, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180125080025o6gxeMJmz9fptha3.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px Helvetica; color: #2131a1; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 17.0px; font: 12.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #2131a1; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #000000} span.s3 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {font: 11.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px 'Helvetica Neue'; text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none; color: #000000; background-color: transparent} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 14.0px; font: 12.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #2131a1; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; background-color: #ffffff} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 12.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Numeral Sofa by Savage for CARMENES</h3><p>在上周的科隆国际家具展上，西班牙高端家居品牌 CARMENES 推出了 Numeral 系列模块化沙发，设计方是西班牙设计工作室 Savage。Numeral 沙发造型低调，线条简洁，弯曲圆润的沙发脚，搭配线条利落的金属腿，灵感源自 1950 年代的沙发风格，却又融入了当代设计元素。模块化系统包括一系列不同尺寸的作为选择，可以自定义配置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204441dFTceWm82xZtyr5S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.564844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801212044140yTniYJulG9dagNI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.597656\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204414197EkJ3pC4uqjx6d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204414yzqFPk2Ve1nOT470.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.014844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Numeral Tables by Savage for CARMENES</h3><p>同样是来自西班牙高端家居品牌 CARMENES 的新品，与 Numeral 沙发同系列的桌子，可以说和沙发共同构成了定义起居室的最佳组合，金属制造的桌子分为长方形、圆形和正方形三种形状，可以组合排列，也可以单独使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204502TLAWcXylq1vZD2Ou.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.482031\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204503sIa0FyxRYNG6vBMK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703906\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204505XfajGcCwk4pxgD0H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204506kX4FneTNQAqU8itL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.207031\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Homeware &amp; Apparel Collection by Patternity &amp; John Lewis</h3><p>总部位于伦敦的平面设计公司 Patternity 与英国连锁品牌 John Lewis 合作，推出了家居用品和女装新品合作款，包括单色款、几何重复元素以及其他更流畅的图案元素。整个系列包括紧身裤、T 恤、靠垫、毛巾、地毯和床上用品等等，这也是 John Lewis 首次涉足时尚和家居领域。</p><p>尽管是设计师合作款，但 John Lewis 还是主打性价比，希望为日常生活探索更多有趣的，具有艺术感的单品。John Lewis 的家居设计负责人 <a href=\"https://www.itsnicethat.com/news/patternity-john-lewis-homeware-fashion-product-design-190118\" rel=\"nofollow\">Philippa Prinsloo 表示</a>，“设计师以客户的生活为出发点，设计出符合当今生活方式的产品。我喜欢他们的冷静和目的感，这是很实在的，同时保留了有思想的设计感。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801212045382yEVQGjuOeMp9Fwg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204538UJMqiOzjnrWsZFEw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400552\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204538y82niFwWEtqpZYaD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400552\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201801212045402kGndeKFIM4HmuSY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400552\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204541X58oQjT1NkOeahYp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204543eg1h95NX7TIswdbA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.400552\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kennedy Weekender by Oliver Cabell</h3><p>美国轻奢手袋初创品牌 Oliver Cabell 由内部团队设计，随后直接在意大利合作工厂内生产，终端只通过线上直销。品牌的垂直销售模式切除了代理等中间环节，号称透明定价。</p><p>这款名为 Kennedy Weekender 的短途旅行包，由意大利小牛皮和优质意大利棉制成，外设两个拉链口袋，内部也设有一个拉链口袋和两个敞口式口袋，做工细节极其讲究，售价 285 美元，<a href=\"https://olivercabell.com/products/heathrow-weekender?variant=7662480581\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204809my53hECG7Vt4wQbY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204721sFXka6bendUAGLiQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204723UXzFHpgoSea37x9n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751429\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204725zF7RkPXp3isQ5qlW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750977\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204726FqdZtVYMERGzmiru.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750977\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>SLY Armchairs by Italo Pertichini for Adrenalina</h3><p>去年，意大利家具品牌 Adrenalina 在米兰设计周期间推出了设计师 Italo Pertichini 主刀的 SLY 座椅系列，最近他们为这一系列推出了全新配色。椅背部分的大面积弧形设计试图将用户包裹其中，提供一部分隐私功能，中间还藏有镂空的细节，又成为窥视外部世界的一道窗口。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204826JM6zsd03ZWK1fNmC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.839063\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204826bqJLEPUc4N2W6Fgo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204826YeXlwhDugVUybCAN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664063\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204827QyNnkYfm3PEeK5bl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.889844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204827SH8sDFv0zrbEd63j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.875000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Falster Smartwatch by SKAGEN</h3><p>手表品牌 SKAGEN 推出新品 Falster 智能手表。很长时间以来，SKAGEN 都以高颜值而著称，在机械零件的经典手表机罩下隐藏一些可穿戴的专用传感器，比如测量你的步数或是心率，但又不似智能手表那般功能多样。</p><p>但这款 Falster，内置了高通 Wear 2100 和 Android Wear 2.0 系统，它配备了全尺寸的 42 毫米表壳，保留了 SKAGEN 一贯以来的简约时尚外观，用皮革或金属表带。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204849mpnUBNcuOExloVF0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204849Cukqzw4fYGS8gVJd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.788776\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204849YTiKF3JrpIQGClPL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.686719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20180121204850Bwdjm1SpxgtZfQz0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.463281\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}